column4: In August, total spot trading volumes rose 36.8% to $1.91tn. The Top-Tier spot volumes increased 41.6% to $1.80tn and Lower-Tier spot volumes decreased 12.3% to $108bn. Top-Tier exchanges now represent 94.3% of total spot volume.
